#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1997
msgid "EU"
msgstr "UE"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1969
#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1990
